rows.label: tlk001801_06_msg0001
rows.name:
How is Hana's Judgement Day mode
working out for you, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk001801_06_msg0002
rows.name:
When I made that, I witnessed
the moment I surpassed my
own father, mo...

rows.label: tlk001801_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Before I knew it, Tora grew up
and became a fine engineer, mo.

rows.label: tlk001801_06_msg0004
rows.name:
B-but no, no! I don't plan
on losing just yet, mo.

rows.label: tlk001801_06_msg0005
rows.name:
This time for sure, I want to
create a Young Justice mode
smaller than a water flea, mo!
